    <description>
        <p>Provide a simple Dark Souls OST streamer for you to enjoy the peaceful or agitated side of Lordran.</p>
        <p>Chose from:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Dark Souls: Prepare to Die Edition</li>
            <li>Dark Souls 2: Scholar of the First Sin</li>
            <li>Dark Souls 3 + DLCs</li>
        </ul>
       <p>Dark Souls OST Player is based on Python + GStreamer.</p>
       <p>Dark Souls OST Player is open source software under the MIT Licence. Sources are available at: https://github.com/Neph-IO/dsost</p>
    </description>

    <url type="homepage">https://github.com/Neph-IO/dsost</url>

